{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙是特种部队第七团队的精英战士，在酒吧与宿敌黑面神一伙发生冲突并轻松获胜，随后与酒吧皇后周香媚共度一夜。次日被军机秘书郑翠芝公报私仇，以参加科学实验为由押往科学院。在地下深层的秘密实验室里，马克所长向他揭示了时空穿越计划——利用时间炉将他送回公元前246年的秦朝。项少龙虽极力反对，仍被强行注射药物并送入时间炉。然而实验过程中力场失控，时间炉发生剧烈爆炸，整座实验室瞬间化为分子灰烬，无人生还。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_bao",
      "speaker_name": "犀豹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有多少人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "小张",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "龙哥，快给我们出这口鸟气！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_man_niu",
      "speaker_name": "蛮牛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是八四一部队的教官黑面神，竟斗胆挑惹我们的冰霜靓女。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扶他们进去，让小弟表演一下身手！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "speaker_name": "黑面神",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一个对一个，还是一起上！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "text": "对付你这种角色，何须费神，悉听尊便。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "小张",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小心！这小子很厉害。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁观者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人怕了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_man_niu",
      "speaker_name": "蛮牛",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "黑面神后面那两个人是本地拳击馆最辣的两个冠军拳手，他们这次是有备而战，存心落我们的颜面。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_man_niu",
      "text": "叫他们袖手旁观，我有信心单独解决这三个家伙。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "speaker_name": "黑面神",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！我已经容忍你很久了，上次你在野猫卡拉ＯＫ打伤了我们十多人，今天我便和你算算旧账。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "text": "给我来瓶鲜奶，让我教训完黑面神后解渴。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑面神的人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子要使出吃奶力气哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hei_mian_shen",
      "text": "来！一起上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！你不要得意！我会要你好看！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "周香媚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要带人家到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "text": "当然是回家啦！我怎够钱付酒店昂贵的租金。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项队长，你还有十五分钟时间梳洗，宪兵部的装甲车在大门外等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "周香媚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "倒霉鬼！快来嘛！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "你吓唬我吗？打场架又会是这么严重的大事件？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁说和打架有关？是科学院那边要我们体能最好的特种人员去做实验，我见你昨晚那么英勇，体能好得那么惊人，便向指挥官推荐你，指挥官已签发命令哩！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "但今天我仍在放假啊！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的项队长，没有任务才可以放假嘛！军人是二十四小时都属于国家的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "唉！昨晚我这么勇猛，还不是为了你，你是真不知还是假不知呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_xiang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "周香媚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你在和谁说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你骗人！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "text": "我怎么会骗你？我项少龙日日夜夜都想着你，只是没说出来罢了！你可知道，我……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_cui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "郑翠芝",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好了！迟些再说！最多你只做一天的实验白老鼠，下次我找其他人去好了。快换衣服。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是病人，自己可以走路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi",
      "speaker_name": "护士",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乖乖地做个好孩子，我不但知道你不是病人，还知道你比一条牛还强壮。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi",
      "text": "嘿！你叫什么名字，怎样可以找到你？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ting",
      "speaker_name": "方廷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我是方廷博士，她是谢枝敏博士，我们是这个时空计划的总工程师马克所长的助手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_ting",
      "text": "这是怎么一回事？至少应该告诉我来这里是干什么吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_zhi_min",
      "speaker_name": "谢枝敏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！一切都很安全，至于细节，马所长会亲自告诉你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ting",
      "speaker_name": "方廷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "军人的天职是为国家服务，项队长能成为时空计划第一个真人试验品，应该感到荣幸才对。来！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我是马克所长，项队长感觉如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "感觉就像一头被送往屠宰场的畜牲，还不知道那是宰猪还是宰牛的屠宰场。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项队长真会说笑。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你对我们国家哪段时期的历史比较熟悉一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "这和做实验有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先回答我的问题。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "我对历史知道得不多，不过最近看过《秦始皇》那部电影，对他的阿房宫和放纵的声色生活非常羡慕，又看过几本关于战国和秦始皇的书……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿！这就行了，就是大秦帝国，公元前二百四十六年秦王政即位的第一年。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "我的天！你在说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "朋友！你不知道你有多么幸运，竟能成为人类历史上第一个返回过去的人。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你有没有看电视上那部叫《时光隧道》的影集，你看！眼前正是伟大的时光隧道，这再不是一个梦想，而是一个事实，很快地，我们将会改变人类对时空的所有观念……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "不要说笑了，告诉我到这里来究竟是做什么实验？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "待会儿你会被送进时间炉里，只要我按下一个按钮，装在炉底的氢聚变反应炉会在三十六小时内积聚足够的能量，在炉内的热核里产生一个能量的黑洞，破开时空，那时磁场输送器会把你送回公元前的世界，你说那是多么奇妙的一件事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "你不是在说笑吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然不是说笑，我已经成功地把十二只白老鼠、两只猴子送回过去，又安然无恙地把它们带回来，只可惜它们不能告诉我是否确实到过那里去，和身处其间的感受，所以才要请军部供应我们体能最好的战士来做实验品，那个人就是你项少龙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ma_ke",
      "text": "我不同意，我要立即脱离军队。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要慌张，你只会在那里停留不到十秒钟的时间，就像作了一个短暂的梦，我只要你记着梦里曾发生过的事。可以注射了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_jiu_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "研究员",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "时间炉内的力能异常地攀升，请马所长指示是否应立即关闭能源？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ke",
      "speaker_name": "马克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "紧急措施第五项，立即执行！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 343
    }
  ],
